        "text": "۞ يَوْمَ يَجْمَعُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلرُّسُلَ فَيَقُولُ مَاذَآ أُجِبْتُمْ ۖ قَالُوا۟ لَا عِلْمَ لَنَآ ۖ إِنَّكَ أَنتَ عَلَّٰمُ ٱلْغُيُوبِ",
        "translationEn": "[Be warned of] the Day when Allah will assemble the messengers and say, \"What was the response you received?\" They will say, \"We have no knowledge. Indeed, it is You who is Knower of the unseen\"",
